NUMBER 2347 
NAME Murky Depths 
REGION 62
CHANNEL 777
FIXED_LIGHT
UNDERSEA
EXIT U 2344
EXIT N 2349
EXIT S 2350
*DESCRIPTION_START
A few feet out from the ledge, the ground drops away below your feet,
leaving no choice but to swim. It's nearly impossible to tell if the
ground is a right below your toes, or another thousand feet below.
Light flashes briefly around you, but the heaviness of the water makes
it even more difficult to see anything clearly.
*DESCRIPTION_END
MONSTER_GROUP 45
;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
