NOUNDEF 1555 porpoise
INUMBER 1957
NAME 1555
VOLUME 1
WEIGHT 1
TURNABLE
FLIPABLE
IFPREVERB HUG -1
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR RNUM = 2350
    ECHO PLAYER You wrap your arms tightly around the porpoise and it chitters at you. Suddenly it streaks upward, dragging you with it!
    ECHO OTHERS %n hugs a porpoise, and it streaks up out of sight.
    MOVE 2351
  ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER You wrap your arms tightly around the porpoise and it chitters at you playfully.
    ECHO OTHERS %n hugs a porpoise and it chitters playfully.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
EQUAL ITEMVAL1 RNUM
SUB ITEMVAL1 2300
IFVAR ITEMVAL1 < 0
  REMOVEITEM -1
  ECHO PLAYER With a final chitter, the porpoise slaps the water with its tail and arcs into the air before disappearing.
ENDIF
